Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I, Paragraph B(a) (b) and (c) | Description :The recipient shall cause ABC and AASANA tocarry out the project in accordance with (i) IPP, (ii) Resettlement Plan, and (iii) Environmental Management Plans | Frequency:Yearly
